===Etymology===
From Old French ''[[theatre#Old French|theatre]]'' (modern ''[[théâtre]]'') or Latin ''[[theatrum]]'', from [[Ancient Greek]] '''[[θέατρον]]''' (''theatron'') "a place for viewing", from '''[[θεάομαι]]''' (''theaomai'') "to see, to watch, to observe".

